'''Solohan the Deceiver''' was a [[Deity/Legends|deity]] of the [[Cult of Varn]] based on the [[Smuggler/Legends|smuggler]] [[Han Solo/Legends|Han Solo]]. He was a messenger of the gods who turned to evil, and was taken back to the heavens on his [[Millennium Falcon/Legends|great flying chariot]] as punishment for his blasphemy. He was aided by a [[Chewbacca/Legends|sinister, furry demon]].

